    "We mainly discuss three social issues, one is HDT regulation, another is ethics and privacy, the third one is trust and transparency.",
    "Finally, due to the unique human thinking and cognition, machine intelligence and cognitive simulation could be considered to optimize HDT.",
    "Technology issues• Artificial Intelligence AI is one of the underlying core technologies of HDT, mainly used for data processing and system optimization [13].",
